<p1 id="tribute-info">
  
  <h3>Facts About Barney</h3>
  
  <ul>
  <li> Barney Stinson is a character played by Neil Patrick Harris in the TV Show How I Met Your Mother 2005-2014  </li>
  <li>Barney appeared in 208 epsisodes as the womanizing user who frequenly scores with attactive woman by running plays from his "Play Book"</li>
    <li>Barney is "Best Friends" with Ted Mosby whom he met at a urinal at MacClaren's Pub.  Later in the series Ted will develop an even closer bond with Ted's real best friend Marshall Erikson</li>
    <li>Barney works for Goliath National Bank or GNB.  When asked what he does for GNB is his reply is always "Please".  We later find our that its an acronymn for, <u>P</u>roivde <u>L</u>egal <u>E</u>xculpation <u>A</u>nd <u>S</u>ign <u>E</u>verything. 
      <li>Barney falls in love with Robin damaging his friendship with Ted, who also loves Robin.  In the end Barney executes a play from his Play Book called the Robin in order to propose to her</li>
    <li>Barney has many catch phrases on the show but his most famous are Legen...wait for it...dary Lengendary and Suit Up!!</li>
    
    </ul>
  
  </p1>
